flowchart TD
  U[User] --> A[Agent / LLM Orchestrator]

  A -->|Tool call (MCP)| GW[Context Gateway MCP Server
(PreToolUse hook)]

  subgraph Sandbox[Isolated subprocess sandbox]
    EX[execute: run script/CLI
(JS/TS/Python/Shell/Go/Rust...)]
    ART[(Artifacts: logs, snapshots, CSVs
NOT sent to LLM context)]
    EX --> ART
  end

  GW --> EX
  EX -->|stdout / small JSON| GW
  GW -->|compressed result (<1KB typical)| A

  subgraph KB[Local Knowledge Base]
    IDX[index: chunk markdown by headings
keep code blocks]
    FTS[(SQLite FTS5 + BM25 + stemming)]
    IDX --> FTS
  end

  GW -->|fetch_and_index(URL)| IDX
  A -->|search(query)| GW
  GW -->|exact snippets + headings| A

  A --> R[Response]
